### Code Complexity

* 
=> https://pypi.org/project/lizard/ lizard
* 
=> https://pypi.org/project/radon/ radon

#### Lizard

`lizard -x'*/tests/*' -l python -w src`

#### Radon

```
radon cc --min B --average --total-average src
radon mi --min B src
```

